<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ways to Style an HTML Document</title>
    <!-- Internal CSS -->
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .internal-style {
            color: #007bff;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .external-style {
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: green;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
    <!-- External CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Ways to Add Styles to an HTML Document</h1>
    </header>

    <main>
        <!-- Inline CSS -->
        <section>
            <h2 style="color: purple; font-size: 1.5em;">1. Inline CSS</h2>
            <p style="background-color: #eee; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ccc;">
                This text is styled using <strong>inline CSS</strong>. The styles are applied directly to the HTML element using the <code>style</code> attribute.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Internal CSS -->
        <section>
            <h2 class="internal-style">2. Internal CSS</h2>
            <p>
                This text is styled using <strong>internal CSS</strong>. The styles are defined within the <code>&lt;style&gt;</code> element in the document's <code>&lt;head&gt;</code>.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- External CSS -->
        <section>
            <h2 class="external-style">3. External CSS</h2>
            <p>
                This text is styled using <strong>external CSS</strong>. The styles are defined in a separate CSS file linked to the document using the <code>&lt;link&gt;</code> element.
            </p>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>




















styles.css



h2.external-style {
    font-size: 1.5em;
    font-style: italic;
}
p {
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 10px 0;
}
